wjt - slider widget
===================
wjt is a slider widget for X.


Requirements
------------
In order to build wjt you need the Xlib header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (wjt is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install wjt
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running wjt
-----------
See the man page for details.
